title.narrative: Uttar Pradesh Sodic Lands Reclamation III Project

description.narrative: The project development objective (PDO) is to increase agricultural productivity of degraded lands in selected areas of UP. The objective would be achieved by reversing water-induced land degradation, enhancing soil fertility, and improving the provision of agriculture support services.
